A different way to get to the number of adults with less clicks.
```
        init_count = self.find_element_by_xpath(
            '//*[@id="xp__guests__inputs-container"]/div/div/div[1]/div/div[2]/span[1]'
        ).text
        init_count = int(init_count)

        if init_count > count:
            decrease_button = self.find_element_by_css_selector(
                'button[aria-label="Decrease number of Adults"]'
            )
            while (init_count > count):
                decrease_button.click()
                init_count -= 1

        if init_count < count:
            increase_button = self.find_element_by_css_selector(
                'button[aria-label="Increase number of Adults"]'
            )
            while (init_count < count):
                increase_button.click()
                init_count += 1
```

